abstract.0: Start your Oracle OpenWorld off right by attending this homeroom session for Oracleâ€™s PeopleSoft. In this session learn what you need to know to maximize your event experience: find the great PeopleSoft content available at Oracle OpenWorld including key messages, must-see sessions, and more. Get insight into the new and existing information sources Oracle offers for PeopleSoft beyond, from videos and planning tools to concept portal pages and blogs. Learn what resources exist, where to find them, and what to use them for.
abstract.1: In this Homeroom session, discover more Oracle ERP Cloud and Oracle EPM Cloud activities at Oracle OpenWorld that will help you have the most impact on your business, as well as make connections with peers and experts. The goal of this Homeroom session is to help you make the most of your experience at the conference.
